data.description: Perfectly Paradise indeed!  Created for nature lovers... Nestled on 5 private fenced acres in a dead-end street, featuring lush pastures, lovely Lemon Grass Garden, 2 paddocks and wooded area, cross ties, cross fence, and a beautiful lively pond view with plenty of fish and wildlife. Amongst this wonderful setting, seat a beautiful concrete block adorned with wood facia to add to the rustic country design, comfortable and spacious ranch style home 3 bedroom, 2 baths plus office completes this paradise along with its serene country lifestyle waiting for you.... Short driving distant from shopping, restaurants, great schools, riding trails, Sarasota Polo Club, beaches and other wonderful city amenities that Lakewood Ranch, Sarasota and Bradenton have to offer.... Truly a Paradise indeed.... Don't miss out on this special once in the lifetime opportunity.
